'''Ekalavya Model Residential School''' or '''EMRS''' is a model [[residential school]] for tribal people.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://articles.economictimes.indiatimes.com/2011-02-01/news/28430255_1_multi-pronged-strategy-naxal-military-helicopters| title=Naveen demands central help to tackle Naxal menace| last=Patnaik| first=Nageshwar| date=1 February 2011| work=The Economic Times| accessdate=13 November 2011}}</ref> It was established by the [[Ministry of Tribal Affairs|Tribal Ministry]], Government of India.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.hindu.com/thehindu/holnus/000200811181821.htm| title=Orissa seeks long term plan to solve Kandhamal problem| date=18 November 2008| work=The Hindu News| accessdate=13 November 2011}}</ref>

